Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:11.73,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,In the State of Qin and the State of Wei's fierce battle, Xin and Lun Hu have faced off once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:11.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）秦国(しんこく)と魏国(ぎこく)との\N激戦の中で 再び対峙(たいじ)した信(しん)と輪虎(りんこ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:18.02,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Which one will surpass their limits\N and continue on their path?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界を超え 己の道を貫き通すのは\N果たして どちらか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人の熱き思いが今 火花を散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:22.42,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,These two's heated emotions are now making sparks fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:28.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗(れんぱ)）さっさと下りてこい！\N一騎打ちでカタをつけるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:26.07,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Hurry and get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:28.84,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,We'll settle this one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:32.59,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I don't mind fighting empty handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちは素手でも かまわんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:33.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁(もうごう)）人の おちょくり方も\N変わっておらぬわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.63,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The way he teases people hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それは それで うれしいわい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:39.85,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,But I'm actually quite happy with this. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:42.08,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:42.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）よし 始めるぞ！\N（馬令）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:42.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Take your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,配置に就け！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:48.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）全兵を呼べ！ 急げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Call all soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.73,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:54.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノリ悪し ハハハハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:51.39,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Looks like he's not game for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:59.49,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.4\c&H000000&\pos(600,105)}The Final Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）ンンッ…\Nやはり廉頗１人ではなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I knew Lian Po wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:29.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだろう…\N（兵士）どうなってんだ？ これは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:28.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's going to happen here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:38.46,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,The primary purpose of the headquarters made up of the Great General and his staff officers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:38.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）大将と その幕僚からなる\N本営の最大の目的にして 責務とは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:44.37,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,is to establish a map of the entire war and lead their army to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その戦いの全体図を描ききり\N自軍を勝利に導くことである
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:50.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 双方の描いた その設計図の\N作りは 共通する部分もあった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:50.50,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,And that blueprint the two sides created have certain parts in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:54.69,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,While Meng Ao and Lian Po were enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:52.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁と廉頗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:58.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵同士でありながらも ２人の心は\N極めて近く寄り添っていたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:58.51,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,each ones's thoughts were exceedingly close to the other's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:04.01,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,The map of this war I drew... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:04.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）\Nわしが描いた今回の戦の全体図
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:08.52,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,had the main army, the central army, as a shield... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本軍である中央軍をあえて盾とし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗の中央軍の攻撃を\Nまずは 徹底的に受け止める
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:14.52,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,and would first thoroughly stop Lian Po's central army's attack. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:23.26,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,And in that interim, the two mighty generals Huan Ji and Wang Jian would form our main attack {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして その間に 強力な攻撃力を\N持つ桓騎(かんき) 王翦(おうせん)の両副将を―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:30.21,Kingdom - Titles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,405)}Qin{Blue. Just use one somewhere on each side.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:30.21,Kingdom - Titles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(852,279)}Wei {Green}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:25.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻撃の主軸とし 左右から進撃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.52,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,and charge from the left and the right. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:30.21,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,They would then crush their oppositions and push onward to the enemy headquarters. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:30.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相対する魏国軍を撃破し\Nそのまま本陣を狙う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:39.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が魏国軍の攻撃の主力は\Nあくまでも中央の輪虎軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.20,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,The main force of my State of Wei Army's attack {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.55,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,is undoubtedly the Lun Hu Army in the center. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:44.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 左右の軍を\N敵副将たちに当たらせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.53,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,However {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:45.01,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,if I have my armies on the left and right attack their respective Vice Generals, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,撃破 もしくは押し込みを図る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:48.56,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,they will crush or push though their opponents. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:52.69,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,They will then turn inwards to Meng Ao's headquarters. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\Nそのまま 蒙驁本陣に回り込む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:54.94,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,In other words...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:59.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）中央 左右と\N３つの戦場から組み立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:59.44,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I have constructed the three battlefields of the center, the left, and the right.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）同じ戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:02.45,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,The same strategy. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:06.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）\Nまあ これは誰でも思い至ること
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:06.77,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Of course, this something anybody could think up.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:11.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 問題は ここからだ\N（蒙驁）その対応は分かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.28,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,The real issue is what comes next.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:11.46,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,The way those battlefields are being handled differ.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは 守りに徹するように命じた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.46,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I've ordered my army to {\i1}defend{\i0} with all their strength.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）わしは攻めに出た
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.46,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I've issued commands to {\i1}attack{\i0}.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.11,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,And we've won, of course.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:28.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄峰(げんぽう)は 早々に散ったものの―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:28.39,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,While Xuan Feng was taken out fairly early,  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:33.39,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Jie Zifang later advanced.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのあとに介子坊(かいしぼう)の軍が押し寄せた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:40.51,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,When they enter battle, the State of Qin Army's main force, the Huan Ji Army, has been silent.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:38.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つぶし合いに入って\N秦国軍の主力の一方 桓騎軍は―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沈黙した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけでも こちらは優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.53,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,That alone is enough to give us predominance.   {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:49.24,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,And what's tilted the state of war above all is...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:51.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして何よりも 戦局を大きく\N傾かせたのは 右の戦場だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.57,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,the right battlefield.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:57.46,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,When I dispatched the army directly under me, the Wang Jian Army retreated far back. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:57.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わし直属の軍が出たことで\N王翦軍は 後方深くに後退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.13,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,No... they ran.   {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,否… 逃げていきおった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:07.39,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Meng Ao, wouldn't you say that's a pretty big miscalculation on your part?  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:07.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁よ さすがに\Nこれは大誤算ではなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:12.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りの もう片方の主軸が\N機能を失ったうえに―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:12.95,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Not only has the other side of your main force which you're relying on lost its ability to function, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:16.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしに 本陣背後を\N突かせてしまったのだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:16.77,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I've pierced the back of your headquarters.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.91,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,The reason I gave Bai Guixi the title of Great General {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが 白亀西(はくきさい)に大将を譲ったのも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この図を\N初めから思い描いていたからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:24.52,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,is because I expected this map to play out from the beginning. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.84,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,After that, all I needed was for Lun Hu to break through the center. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:29.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは輪虎が中央を突破すればいい\Nわしは背後を突く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.53,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Then I would attack the rear. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:34.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前後から\N挟み撃ちで 本陣を落とすだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:34.04,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,With a pincer attack from the front and the rear, we would take down the headquarters. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:41.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）フォフォフォ…\Nうろたえることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.66,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,There's no need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:45.05,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Against him, I am always a "loser".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの前では\Nいつでも わしは敗者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬公）殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.38,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:52.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）本陣の全軍を後ろに回せ\N（馬令）ぜ… 全軍を？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.33,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Send all of the headquarter's armies to the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A-All armies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:56.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）しかし それでは 正面の\N中央軍が抜かれたときの手だてが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:56.56,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But then what means of defense will we have when the central army is penetrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かまわぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.56,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I'm not concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗よ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:11.31,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po, I've lost to you every time in the past. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:13.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぬしに負け続けた わしじゃ\Nこうなることも予想はしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.58,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,So I've predicted that something like this would happen. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,予想ができたということは―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.58,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,And having predicted it means... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:21.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,対処ができるということじゃ\Nそして…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:20.24,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I've prepared for it. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.62,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,And so... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この砦(とりで)こそ おぬしを\N討つためだけに築いた いわば―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:28.44,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I constructed this stronghold for the purpose of you attacking it. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.98,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,One might call it... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:33.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁流 対廉頗迎撃布陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:33.95,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,a Meng Ao-style Lian Po intercepting formation! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（従者Ａ）\N裏側に これほどの準備を…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:40.10,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He had this much prepared in the back of his headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（従者Ｂ）守備偏重で\N隙が少ないとは聞いていたがな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:44.00,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'd head he overemphasizes defense and leaves very few gaps, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（従者Ｃ）\Nうん？ いや ちょっと待て
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.55,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ… よく見ろ あの砦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.66,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Take a good look at that stronghold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.49,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's really ill-formed looking and full of unnecessary parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（従者Ｂ）\Nああ なんとも不格好でムダが多い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.84,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,No... this isn't bad. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは悪くない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:03.54,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,With that average style of yours, you've polished up a few things, haven't you, Meng Ao?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,凡人なりに\N多少は練ってあるではないか 蒙驁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.81,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Of course. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:11.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）当たり前じゃ\N長年 考えに考えを重ねた布陣じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:11.70,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,This is a formation I spent many years developing.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:17.52,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,All in order to defeat you if I someday ended up in a battle against you.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの日か\Nおぬしと戦うハメになったとき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぬしを討ち取るためにな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う～む…\Nこれは ひと筋縄では いかんのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.77,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary tactic.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎馬が多すぎる\N半数を馬から下ろせ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:27.96,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,We have too many mounted units. Have half of them get off their horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.82,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The bow unit will act as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弓隊を いつものように！\N盾兵を前に出して矢を受けさせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.62,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Shield soldiers should move forward to block arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.28,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:37.75,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go, Meng Ao. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ～て いくぞ 蒙驁　その首…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:42.29,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I'm going to lop off that head of yours with my own hands. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この手で たたき落としてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充(りじゅう)）あっ！ 敵が動きだしたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.36,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\N廉頗は どこから攻めてくる？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Where is Lian Po attacking from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:48.80,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫(かくきょう)）殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.01,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Come get me, Lian Po! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:56.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来てみよ 廉頗\Nこの砦に入らば 死ぬのは おぬしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.80,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,If you enter this stronghold, the one to die will be you! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁(へき)）周囲の警戒を怠るな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.81,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Maintain vigilance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:04.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々同様 この辺りを\Nさまよっている敵兵がいるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.51,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,There are enemy soldiers wandering around this area just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.31,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）しんがりの役は果たしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.49,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,We've fulfilled our duty as the rear guard, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王翦本隊と はぐれたうえに\N道にも迷った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:14.45,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,but not only have we separated from the Wang Jian main unit, we're also lost. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:19.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの隊も吸収し\Nそれなりの戦力は残っている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:19.45,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,Though we've absorbed other units so we have some considerable fighting power now. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.71,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,We need to get back to the front line quickly... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く前線に復帰せねば…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壁さま あれは…\N（壁）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Bi! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁将軍の本陣… こんな所まで\N迷って来てしまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.82,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,General Meng Ao's headquarters? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.01,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,We drifted all the way here? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:46.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まさか\N敵に迫られているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.60,Kingdom-Thought,Bi,0,0,0,,I... It can't be! It's being approached by enemies?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:06.25,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lian Po is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗が動いたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）た… 隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:10.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,C-Captain! Lian Po is heading this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗が こちらに！\N（隊長）あ… 慌てるな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:12.26,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,D-Don't lose your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:16.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隊長）フン… バカめ\Nかかりおったな 廉頗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.82,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,That fool! We've got you now, Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:22.28,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,One of the oldest tricks in the book is to attack from the side to avoid an arrow onslaught.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:22.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隊長）矢の雨を避けるため\N端から攻めるは定石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:27.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから あらかじめ\N側面の林に弓隊を隠している
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:26.77,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,And in anticipation of that, we hid a bow unit in the forest on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正面と側面から矢を受ければ\Nいかに廉頗とて ひとたまりもない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.77,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,If he's pelted with arrows both from the front ant the sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.19,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,even Lian Po won't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:36.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハッ！\Nさすが“伝説の武将”廉頗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.58,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from the legendary military commander, Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,既に 戦が古いわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.93,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,His fighting style is outdated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,射(う)て！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.77,Kingdom-Main,Cap,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A-Are they insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隊長）き… 気は確かか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ 味方に矢を打ち込む！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Why are they firing arrows at their allies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:55.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord, what in the world is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充）殿 これは 一体…\N（蒙驁）側面の林は―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:09:00.72,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The forest on the side has already fallen into the enemy's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,既に 敵の手に落ちたのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒッ… ヒイッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隊長たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.16,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,L-Lian Po just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充）れ… 廉頗が あっさりと\N（馬令）１段目が抜かれるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.95,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,got up the first step that easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.86,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,The right edge was defeated as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:19.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）右の端も やられた！\N（馬令）殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.00,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.00,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Do not panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:23.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,案ずるな　この砦の恐ろしいのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:25.33,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The true ferocity of this stronghold is only just about to become apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここからじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.53,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）\Nいいぞ！ こっちは敵が手薄だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy is short-handed over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）いける！\N（魏兵）蒙驁を八つ裂きにするぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.63,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Let's rip Meng Ao limb from limb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なに！\N（魏兵）これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.41,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:38.34,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.70,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,A dead end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き止まり！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.39,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What's wrong, move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？ 前\N（兵士）何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.31,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い… いかん！ 下がれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.08,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,N-No, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:53.11,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Now, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（弓隊）今だ！ 射て！\N（飛来音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.07,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General... Ally units are being beaten all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:10:01.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近Ａ）将軍… あちこちで\N味方の隊がやられているようです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン…“断道の計”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.15,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,A cut-road plan. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:09.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道を断ち\N敵を追い詰めるための策略だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:09.29,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,It's a strategy where you cut off the roads in order to corner the enemy. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:14.76,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Unlike Wang Jian's fortress that didn't have a vulnerability to it, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:14.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一分の隙もなかった王翦の砦と違い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:19.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁の これは\N一見 不格好で隙だらけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:18.76,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,at first glance, Meng Ao's is clumsily put together and covered with openings. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし いざ上ってみると―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:26.39,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,But it's actually crowded with dead-end roads that you can't see from below. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:26.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下からは見えなかった\N行き詰まる道が ひしめいている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:32.28,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,That is all a part of Meng Ao's plan. If someone is led to one of those areas, it turns into a hunting ground. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 蒙驁が仕組んだもので\Nハマれば 格好の狩り場と化す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁は このワナを砦全体に\N迷路のごとく張り巡らせておるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:38.15,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,He set these up all around his stronghold like a maze. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは 守備の砦にあらず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.12,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,This is no defensive stronghold. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:45.66,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,It is clearly a stronghold for attacking an invading enemy. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:45.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに\N入ってきた敵を迎え撃つ砦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁め　本気で このわしを\N討ち取るつもりのようじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:51.16,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Meng Ao, you old fox, you really intend to take me down, don't you? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:52.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充）すごい！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）敵の足を止めるどころか\N殲滅(せんめつ)している！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.74,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Not only is the enemy being halted, they're being annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\Nさすが 殿自ら考案された布陣だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:58.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You've truly outdone yourself with this formation, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:04.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）\N言われるがままに作り込んだが\Nこんな仕掛けになっておるとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:02.17,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We'd made it just as you instructed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I never expected the traps to be anything like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやはや 驚きました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.78,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm astonished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:11.18,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's truly astonishing is how Lian Po was even prepared for a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:11.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）いや 驚くべきは 廉頗の\N奇襲にまで備えられていたことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.93,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you know, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっておられたのですか？ 殿\Nヤツが来ることが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That he was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:20.80,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,As a military commander, Lian Po has many faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:20.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）廉頗は 武将として\Nいくつもの顔を持っておる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:26.09,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Sometimes he's the "wise general" who makes a detailed plan before the battle starts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）開戦前は\N緻密な計画を立てる知将となり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦が始まれば 戦局の推移を\N直感的に見抜く本能型にもなる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:31.58,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,and sometimes he's the "instinctual type" that detects the changes of the state of battle intuitively after it starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いったん 守備と決め込めば―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:34.32,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,So say he's fighting defensively,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:39.09,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,he becomes a general with an iron-wall defense like he was defending Changping from sieges for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長平(ちょうへい)で２年 籠城したような\N鉄壁の守りの将と化す
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻め時と見れば\N正攻法 奇策を問わず―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.76,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And when he's attacking, he forgets about proper methods and clever schemes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必殺の勢いで攻めてくる剛将となる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.47,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,and becomes a "strong general", one that attacks with lethal force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:52.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして そのときは\N自ら 先陣を切ることも珍しくない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:52.22,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,In those situations, it's not uncommon for him to lead a formation himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.38,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Those times are due to him being a bit too brave for his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:56.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは ヤツが あまりにも\N勇猛であること　そして―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:59.80,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And... those are the rare occasions where he's a showoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:12:01.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希代の目立ちたがり屋ゆえじゃ\Nフォフォフォ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃから読めた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.82,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,So I foresaw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,W-Well done, my lord. Truly admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:07.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）さ… さすが殿です\N敬服いたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:12.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし よくぞ\Nそこまで廉頗のことをご存じで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:11.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But... I'm amazed you know so much about Lian Po...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:20.50,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I know so much about him from my memory of losing to him again and again when I was young. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:18.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若きころ あやつに\N負け続けた記憶からだけでも―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗のことは よく分かっている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それだけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.51,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,But that is not all.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.85,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,It has been about 40 years since I moved to the State of Qin. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国へ移ってから およそ40年\N廉頗と戦うことは一度もなかったが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.76,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Since then, I never once fought Lian Po... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:36.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗の戦いは 全て\Nその内容の隅々まで把握している
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:36.14,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,but I learned every last detail about Lian Po's battles. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その情報収集のために 大金を使い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:39.52,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I used quite a lot of money to collect that information {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:43.32,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,and I even personally went to observe wars at times. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:43.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時には\N自ら ひそかに観戦に向かった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:52.79,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Yes... I've always been watching that Lian Po.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは ずっと―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:58.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗を見てきたのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.79,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs60\be0.4\pos(324,78)}Lian Po
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）こっから先は通さねえぞ！\N（輪虎）フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.13,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you past here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）信！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:06.88,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.26,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin's giving it all he's got over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:12.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信が あんだけやってんだ\N俺たちも負けてらんねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.51,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,so we can't let ourselves get beaten, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）飛信隊に負けるな！\N（兵士）我らの力を示せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.92,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't let the Fexin Unit win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.93,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Show them just how powerful we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこ見てやがる この野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:31.03,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Now... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:31.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The other units are joining with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの隊が我らに合流してきている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近Ｂ）あまり増えると\N行き詰まったとき 戻れぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:45.64,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,If we get too big, we won't be able to turn back if we hit a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:50.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ！\N案ずるな　わしに任せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:50.33,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Don't panic. Leave that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝者）新しい報告が！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.06,Kingdom-Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,A new report!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日 右軍に廉頗将軍が現れ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.32,Kingdom-Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,Yesterday, General Lian Po appeared in the right army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:01.86,Kingdom-Main,Messenger,0,0,0,,And it seems they pushed the Wang Jian Army quite a ways back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:01.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのまま 王翦軍を\N後方深くまで押し込んだもようです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧(りぼく)）うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.69,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,The general went off to the right himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:09.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイネ）将軍自ら 右に？\N（李牧）蒙驁はマズイですね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.70,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Meng Ao looks like he's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:13.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ごろ 廉頗将軍に\N背後を突かれていることでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.07,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,He's probably being attacked by General Lian Po from the rear right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（軍師）やはり\N蒙驁の雪辱は ならぬようですな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:17.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I suppose Meng Ao won't be vindicating his honor, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）\Nうん？ どういうことですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.66,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ？ あっ いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,When Meng Ao lived in the State of Qi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁は 斉(さい)の国にいたころ\N廉頗将軍に負け続けていましたから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.97,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,he had continuous losses against General Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:31.53,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Of course, I have no way of knowing if Lian Po remembers that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗本人が\Nそれを覚えているかは不明ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:36.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁にとっては\N数十年ぶりの雪辱戦であると
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:36.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,but for Meng Ao, this is his first chance at vindication in several decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:40.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ\N私も もともと斉国の人間でしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.68,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You see, I am originally from the State of Qi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.26,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,So I'm actually quite interested in the outcome of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと感慨深いものも…\N言っておりませんでしたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.23,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,り… 李牧さま？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.80,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,L-Lord Li Mu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.54,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,I really wish you'd told me that sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと早く言ってほしかった\N（軍師）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイネ）李牧さま？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.09,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Lord Li Mu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:59.86,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,I think General Lian Po may be an exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）廉頗将軍に限って まず\Nそんなことはないと思いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:05.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強き武将が足をすくわれるとき\Nそこには 必ず油断があります
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:05.52,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,but when strong generals have the rug pulled out from under them, they always let their guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:11.76,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,When I fight, I always do everything I can to make my opponent neglect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:11.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私などは 戦うとき 相手を\N油断させることに力を尽くします
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:17.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし 将軍が\N蒙驁のことを覚えてるとしたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:17.34,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,If the general remembers Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:19.87,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,that is enough to give Meng Ao an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけで 蒙驁は有利です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.04,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Because whichever side wins
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝っていた側は―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手に 相手の器のほどを\N決めつけてしまいますからね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:25.93,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,decides just to what extent the caliber of the opponent he faced was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイネ）どうされました？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.40,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）\Nいや そうです　それだけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.52,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.23,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,That isn't all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:42.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし 蒙驁が廉頗に対して 胸の奥に\N秘めるものを持っているとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:41.91,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,If Meng Ao holds Lian Po as a\N special sort of objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら蒙驁は対廉頗のため―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:49.46,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,then it's possible that he used those 40 years to develop a strategy against Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:49.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,40年は 作戦を練る時間が\Nあったということになります
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.92,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,I don't know what to think now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは分からなくなってきましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:58.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし 蒙驁が廉頗の持つ蒙驁像を\N少しでも上回れば…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:58.83,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,If Meng Ao exceeds the image of the Meng Ao that Lian Po holds by even a little, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（柵を壊す音）\Nこっちじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:06.06,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:12.94,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Dammit! We just can't catch the Lian Po unit in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\Nくそ！ 廉頗隊だけワナにかからぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）ンンッ… 運のいいヤツめ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lucky bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）こっちじゃ！\N（側近Ａ）今度は下へ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.44,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.45,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Now we're moving down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:25.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）あっ またワナをかわした\N（朱可）ま… まさか―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.33,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They dodged another trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.39,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,C-Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.94,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lian Po knows where the traps are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗は\Nワナの場所が分かっているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.63,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:33.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充）それはない！ 下からは\N見えない場所にワナは仕掛けてある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.51,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The traps are set in positions you can't see from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.47,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's not possible he could know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知られるはずが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.47,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Even if he can't see them, he can make a rough prediction of where they're located.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:39.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）見えていなくとも\Nおおまかな予想はできるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.03,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Before he entered the stronghold,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:44.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,砦に入る前\N下から その全容が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.41,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,he saw the whole layout from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:51.02,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Based on the shape of the mountain and the position of the fences, there aren't any suspicious places he can't detect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,柵の位置 山の形状から\N怪しい所を発見できぬこともない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-Then he knew from the first time he saw the stronghold that there were traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:54.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）そ… それでは\N最初に砦を見て ワナがあると？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:59.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）い… いや しかし\N仮に… 仮に予測がついたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:59.03,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,B-But even if he... Even if he did predict where the traps were,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.68,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,once he entered the stronghold, he would no longer be able to see the whole layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度 砦に入れば\Nその全容は見えなくなります
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:10.87,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's impossible to follow the correct route in this complicated maze from memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっときの記憶だけで\Nこの複雑な迷路の―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しい道順を進むことなど―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不可能です！\N（蒙驁）それをやるのが―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:15.55,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,If there's anyone who can do that, it's Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗じゃろうて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンンッ… またワナをかわした\N（郭叫）もう５合目までは来てるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He avoided another trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:22.61,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He's already made it to the fifth level!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:24.87,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All right! Raise the flags!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近Ａ）よ～し 旗を掲げよ！\N将軍の示す道に 間違いはないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:27.92,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The path the general is pointing us in can't be wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.20,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.94,Kingdom-TL Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(166,254)}( Flag - Lian )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）オッ… 見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.16,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:36.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）ついに来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:36.44,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Finally... coming, are you? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:40.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗 わしは十分 知っておるのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:40.48,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I'm well aware, Lian Po. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぬしが\Nこの迷路の攻略図を脳裏に描ききり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:45.04,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I knew full well that you could draw a map for attacking this maze in your mind {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:49.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを狂いなく\N実践できる天才であることを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:49.46,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,and that you could unerringly put it into practice. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:53.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よ～く知っておる　故に―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:52.28,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I know you're a genius. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:53.95,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,And for that reason... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:58.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは\Nおぬしの さかしさを逆手に取る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:58.47,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,that I will use your cleverness against you! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動かせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.34,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\N（朱可）こ… これは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.61,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.50,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,They're creating new routes that lead to traps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワナへとつながる新しい道が\N出来上がった！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:24.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）行った！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.31,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,They're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:26.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かかった！\N（朱可）かかったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.30,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,We've got them! We've got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.14,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近たち）殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.08,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.62,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗 おぬしを討つために―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:36.07,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,the greatest strength of this stronghold I spent 40 years developing {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:35.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,四十数年 練っていた この砦の\N最大の武器は―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:39.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぬしが 事前に攻略した迷路を…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.51,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,is a maze that you overcame in advance. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）ウワッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:47.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）\Nあとから作り替えられることじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.89,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,After that, I just had to reshape it. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）行き止まりだと！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.16,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,A dead end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）ほう…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:55.02,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,射て！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）後ろで…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.03,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I know... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣で何か起こってるのは分かるが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.78,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,that something's going on at the headquarters behind me. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.42,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,But I don't have time to divert attention to that right now. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は そんな所まで気を回せねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:07.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:07.91,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Right now... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.66,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,If I take my eyes off this guy for an instant {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつから目を離せば 即…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.83,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll be send to the next world! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの世行きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:21.42,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）信どの…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:26.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）隣の伍(ご)と共に戦え！\N１歩も引くんじゃないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.59,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Fight with your neighboring Wu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.38,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Don't retreat a single step!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.56,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,The opponents for the mounted units are mounted soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水(そすい)）騎馬隊の相手は騎馬だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歩兵は下がれ！\N皆の者 全てをこの一戦に懸けよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.09,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,All foot soldiers, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.79,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Everyone, we're risking everything on this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）信どの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:43.31,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Lord Xin, leave the direction of the unit to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊の指揮は お任せを\Nその代わり どうか―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.44,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,In exchange, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの手で 輪虎の首を！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.47,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Take down Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いな 渕さん 楚水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.46,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Sorry Mr. Yuan. Chu Shui. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:59.36,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,He did an excellent job stopping my charge. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:20:02.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見事に進撃の足を止められた\N輪動(りんどう)で兵が消耗したせいもあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.21,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,It's partially because of my depletion of soldiers, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.84,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,but it's primarily due to the Feixin Unit's strength. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:06.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何より 止めに入った飛信隊が強い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.59,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Both their mounted soldiers {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎馬も 歩兵も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.35,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,and their foot soldiers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:15.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして それに呼応して\Nほかの隊も戦に加わり奮戦している
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:15.45,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,And in response to that, the other units are fighting even harder. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.36,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,In other words, the source of this part of the State of Qin Army's morale... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:20.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり\Nこの辺り一帯の秦国軍の士気の源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:24.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 飛信隊の隊長 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:24.11,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,is the Feixin Unit Captain, Xin. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:30.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この若者だ　彼が\N実質的に将の役目を担っているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.77,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,This youngster. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.87,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,He's substantially filling the role of general. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.90,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,His fighting strength aside,  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,武の力は ともかく あの年で―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.75,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,his ability to inspire people to this degree at this age {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:39.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これほど人を引き付ける力は\N自分には なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.38,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,is beyond even my own.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.92,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,This youngster truly is... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に この若者は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:49.43,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Do you know just how heavy what\N you're carrying right now is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:50.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 背負っているものの重大さが\N分かっているかい？ 飛信隊の信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.06,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Xin of the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.39,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,If you fall here, the entire State of Qin Army will collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君が倒れれば\Nここの秦国軍は総崩れとなり―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは とっとと蒙驁を討ちに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:58.65,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,And we'll go take down Meng Ao in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.27,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit yammering!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほざいてろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:06.21,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,If {\i1}you{\i0} get slain by {\i1}me{\i0}, then we'll win the central battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえのほうこそ 俺に討たれて\N中央の戦いは こっちの勝ちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャマが―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.54,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Everything that was in the way... is gone! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:18.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えた！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:38.96,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,When you're fighting on horseback, a sword wound to the thigh is fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:37.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬上の剣戟(けんげき)で ももをやられるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,致命的だよ\N（信）クッ…
